text: The IAR-99 is a military training jet aircraft. It was designed and built in Romania by IAR (Industria Aeronautică Română). The IAR-99 was flown for the first time in 1985. It is used only by the Romanian Air Force. == Bibliography == * Frawley, Gerard, The international directory of military aircraft 2002/2003 .
